text: Engelbert Haider (20 April 1922 - 12 November 1999) was an Austrian alpine skier. He competed in three events at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:1999 deaths Category:Austrian male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Austria Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tyrol (state)
